labels.name: dependencies

candidates.body:
Bumps [rustsec](https://github.com/rustsec/rustsec-crate) from 0.23.2 to 0.23.3.
Changelog

Sourced from rustsec's changelog.

0.23.3 (2021-03-08)

Fixed

  • Workaround for stale git refs (#309)
